     7→ *   Consumes domain events from the HoloCanvas Kafka mesh, parses the
     8→ *   payloads (JSON/Protobuf), and routes them to the appropriate
     9→ *   sub-systems (minting engine, bid processor, governance module, etc.).
    10→ *
    11→ *   This is intentionally self-contained so that unit-tests can stub
