    event_dispatcher_register_handler(dispatcher, "MINT_REQUEST", handle_mint_request);
    event_dispatcher_register_handler(dispatcher, "BID", handle_bid);
    event_dispatcher_register_handler(dispatcher, "GOVERNANCE_VOTE", handle_governance_vote);
    event_dispatcher_register_handler(dispatcher, "ORACLE_FEED", handle_oracle_feed);

    // ... worker threads still managed separately ...

    event_dispatcher_run(dispatcher);

    // ... cleanup ...
}
```

### 3. `muse_observer/src/main.c`

**Changes Made:**
- Removed: `kafka_init_consumer()` and `muse_event_loop()` functions
- Removed: Local Kafka polling and message handling
- Added: Service context struct with config and plugin cache
